:{{DIcon|undefined}} Do you know the Supreme Guardian Cyrille?
::<!--Trigger PerformanceE 201140905: Config/Level/Mission/2011409/Act/Act201140905.json-->
::'''Manya:''' ...Mmm, do you mean Cyrille "the Fool"?
::'''Manya:''' Of course. I mean, anyone who's studied a little history has heard of her, right?
::'''Manya:''' What made you suddenly interested in this piece of ancient history? I don't have the time for random trivia right now... There's a huge stack of documents on my desk waiting for my approval.
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} I found something...
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_201340193-->
:::'''Manya:''' Huh? What...
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} I brought something back from Cyrille.
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_201340195-->
:::'''Manya:''' ...Is this some kind of sick joke?
::<!--Custom String Trigger: TalkSentence_201340196-->
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_201340196-->
::'''Manya:''' Ah, okay... I guess, taking a look won't rob me of much time. What is it? Let me have a check, would you?
::'''Manya:''' It's... this...
::'''Manya:''' I'm flabbergasted! You might've just found an incredible antique item...
::'''Manya:''' Based on the ''Belobog Conventions for the Preservation of Ancient Relics'', any antiques found by civilians must be turned over to the Architects for proper preservation. I will have to hold on to this ornament that you've found.
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} What? This is robbery in plain sight!
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Then what's in it for me, huh?
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_201340201-->
::'''Manya:''' Relax, I won't leave you empty-handed. I'm highly confident that this thing is an authentic relic... I'm sure you'll be compensated handsomely.
::'''Manya:''' Mmm, that's right &mdash; do you know much about Belobog's history? You can find out more about Cyrille "the Fool" in this pamphlet. Take it as a souvenir from the Administrative Department.
::<!--Ends the current performance-->
::<!--Custom String Trigger: Talk_201140905-->
;(If {{cx}}<!--SubMission Finish: 101150231-->, {{cx}}<!--SubMission Started: 201140905-->, {{cx}}<!--SubMission Started: 404012705-->, {{cx}}<!--SubMission Started: 404012706-->, {{cx}}<!--SubMission Started: 404012707-->, or {{cx}}<!--SubMission Started: 404012708-->, {{cx}}<!--SubMission Started: 301120204-->, {{cx}}<!--SubMission Started: 301120202-->, {{cx}}<!--SubMission Started: 301120104-->, {{cx}}<!--SubMission Started: 301120102-->, and {{cx}}<!--SubMission Started: 301020103-->)
:{{DIcon}} How have things been?
::'''Manya:''' How have things been? As you can see, it's just the same old, same old. Doing the same work for the same pay.
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Didn't the Town Hall send you to the Underworld?
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_501023753-->
:::'''Manya:''' The Town Hall has already allocated suitable personnel for that. Our administrative officials naturally want to do things by the book.
:::'''Manya:''' Also, the livelihoods of people in the Underworld is not within my job responsibilities. If you want to inquire about the Underworld, please submit your inquiries to an Underworld interim administrative official.
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Oh, I assumed you had been promoted.
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_501023756-->
:::'''Manya:''' ...Sorry to disappoint you. I am still an Administrative Official responsible for handling matters related to civil affairs in the Administrative District.
:::'''Manya:''' Her Excellency, the Supreme Guardian, is optimizing the structure for officials in the Town Hall. But I advise you not to give credence to any gossip before the final results are announced. Everything will be subject to notices posted in Qlipoth Fort.
::<!--Custom String Trigger: TalkSentence_501023759-->
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_501023759-->
::'''Manya:''' Ugh. Citizen... If there is no problem, then please refrain from obstructing my work. In order to ensure the regular connection between the Overworld and Underworld, Town Hall officials at every rank are working overtime. I don't have time for idle chatter.
::<!--Ends the current performance-->
;(If {{cx}}<!--SubMission Finish: 101150231-->, {{cx}}<!--SubMission Started: 201140905-->, {{cx}}<!--SubMission Started: 404012705-->, {{cx}}<!--SubMission Started: 404012706-->, {{cx}}<!--SubMission Started: 404012707-->, or {{cx}}<!--SubMission Started: 404012708-->, {{cx}}<!--SubMission Started: 301120204-->, {{cx}}<!--SubMission Started: 301120202-->, {{cx}}<!--SubMission Started: 301120104-->, {{cx}}<!--SubMission Started: 301120102-->, and {{cx}}<!--SubMission Started: 301020103-->)
:{{DIcon}} There's something else I want to ask.
::'''Manya:''' I just said I'm on break... Fine, if you insist.
::<!--Custom String Trigger: loop_501023703_2-->
::<!--Custom String Listener: loop_501023703_2-->
::{{DIcon|Talk}} What kind of work do you do exactly?
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_501023732-->
:::'''Manya:''' Excellent question! My job involves a little bit of everything, but vital to keeping things running smoothly in Belobog! You could say I'm the unsung hero of the city.
:::'''Manya:''' I'm responsible for grassroots affairs in the Administrative District, listening to basic requests from people, and solving day-to-day issues.
:::{{DIcon|Talk}} In that case, can you hear out my request?
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_501023735 -->
:::'''Manya:''' Of course! But you will need to reserve a slot. My work hours are from 9:00 AM to 12:00 PM, and 2:00 PM to 5:00 PM. I handle administrative and civil affairs during these times.
:::'''Manya:''' I'm currently on break. As a public official, separating professional and private time is of basic importance.
::;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
::{{DIcon|Talk}} How do I make an official appointment?
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_501023738-->
:::'''Manya:''' Please fill out a form at counter 236 on the second floor of Qlipoth Fort. Then have a staff member stamp it at window 35 on the third floor.
:::'''Manya:''' After stamping, please head to window 155 on the first floor and wait in line for the proof of appointment. The formal processing usually takes one month after the appointment has been made.
:::'''Manya:''' To inquire about the specific processes, please consult the window staff when making the appointment.
::;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
::{{DIcon|Talk}} You're just trying to slack off, aren't you?
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_501023742-->
:::'''Manya:''' What would make you think that? But I don't blame you. Many have the same misunderstanding, thinking this is just a job where you can kick your feet up.
:::'''Manya:''' A job where I just "Clock in, drink tea, read the newspaper, chit-chat with colleagues, and stare at the time, waiting to get off." But that's all nonsense.
:::'''Manya:''' Please lose these false impressions of grassroots public officials. Our days are busy ones indeed.
::;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
::{{DIcon|Exit}} Nothing else.
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_501023746-->
